@start_2
title: Example
new-page: true

This is a game of alternate history. Despite being the modification of the semi realistic base game, modification itself allows exploration of nearly-impossible things through *dynamic* mechanics of the game without the elements of make-it-believe or realism lite. 

- @1928_easy: Begin (Easy difficulty)
- @1928_main: Begin (Normal difficulty)
- @1928_hard: Begin (Hard difficulty)
- @1928_historical: Begin (Historical mode)
- @challenge: Challenges and Conditions
- @start_menu: Return back

@challenge

Choose your challenges!

> *Spartacist Victory: [? if spartac_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if spartac_challenge != 1: OFF ?]* <br> 
> *Randomized World: [? if inverted_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if inverted_challenge != 1: OFF ?]* <br>
> *Randomized Ideologies: [? if inverted_ideos = 1: ON ?][? if inverted_ideos != 1: OFF ?]* <br>
> *Gang: [? if gang_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if gang_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*<br>
> *Modern Democracy: [? if dem_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if dem_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*<br>
> *New Party: [? if new_partei_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if new_partei_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*<br>
> *Agrarian Revolution: [? if peasant_revolution = 1: ON ?][? if peasant_revolution != 1: OFF ?]*<br>
> *Camarillamulator: [? if cmr_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if cmr_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*<br>
> *Last Stand: [? if ls_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if ls_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*<br>
> *Dice: [? if dice_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if dice_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*<br>
> *Duel: [? if duel_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if duel_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*<br>
> *Hindenburg: [? if hindenburg_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if hindenburg_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*<br>
> *FPTH: [? if fptp_variable = 1: ON ?] [? if fptp_variable = 0: OFF ?]*<br>
> *Street Law: [? if street_law_challenge = 1: ON ?] [? if street_law_challenge = 0: OFF ?]*<br>
> *Base Gamemode Trust Me: [? if april_challenge = 1: ON ?][? if april_challenge != 1: OFF ?]*<br>

- @separator_3: Main Modes:
- @spartacus: Spartacist Victory!
- @bauern: Agrarian Revolution
