SPD is newly formed party of the small unions and some social democrats. Can you make it prosper?

- @new_2: True
- @new_3: False
- @challenge: Back.

@new_2
view-if: new_partei_challenge = 0
on-arrival: new_partei_challenge = 1
go-to: new

Turned on!

@new_3
view-if: new_partei_challenge = 1
on-arrival: new_partei_challenge = 0
go-to: new

Turned off!


@democracy

= Modern Democracy

Turn your Weimar into modern democracy with just one trick!

- @democracy_2: True
- @democracy_3: False
- @challenge: Back.

@democracy_2
view-if: dem_challenge = 0
on-arrival: dem_challenge = 1
go-to: democracy

Turned on!

@democracy_3
view-if: dem_challenge = 1
on-arrival: dem_challenge = 0
go-to: democracy

Turned off!

@spartacus

= Spartacus

Spartacists have won and only left wing parties remain, as others are banned. SAPD and SRPD are formed by the start.

- @spartacus_2: True
- @spartacus_3: False
- @challenge: Back.

@spartacus_2
view-if: spartac_challenge = 0
on-arrival: spartac_challenge = 1
go-to: spartacus

Turned on!

@spartacus_3
view-if: spartac_challenge = 1
on-arrival: spartac_challenge = 0
go-to: spartacus

Turned off!

@gang

= Gang

Everyone, even splitters are here! Let's see how party dynamics will go. New 28+ parties will be added to the game. Best paired with inverted world.

- @gang_2: True
- @gang_3: False
- @challenge: Back.

@gang_2
view-if: gang_challenge = 0
on-arrival: gang_challenge = 1
go-to: gang

Turned on!

@gang_3
view-if: gang_challenge = 1
on-arrival: gang_challenge = 0
go-to: gang

Turned off!

